<h2 class="bold font-l">Pinkie's Singing Telegrams</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Pinkie delivers singing telegrams to her friends as invitations to her alligator Gummy's first birthday. </p>
</div>
</div>
